704523f-a.title: Brooklyn: Fulton Street - Hanover Place
704523f-a.text:
Fulton Street, south side, at adjoining and east of Hanover Place.
Also seen is Hanover Place, east side, south of Fulton Street. Overhead on
Fulton Street, is the Fulton Street Elevated Lines of the B.M.T. (On Han-
over Place, next to the Sterling Piano Co., S.S. Kresge has a department
store beyond which Grove Place has been cut through, since this view was
taken.)
About 1906.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
